articles.title: As the WNBA season tips off, here are 4 of our biggest questions - NPR
articles.description: Will a new-look Indiana Fever contend in Caitlin Clark's second year? Will A'ja Wilson win a record 4th MVP? And the biggest question of all: Can the league as a whole build on last season's success?
articles.content:
By nearly every measure, last year's WNBA season was a tremendous success.
